text: Kuchergich () is a rural locality (a village) in Ismailovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 67 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Dyurtyuli, 2 km from Ismailovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Kuchergich
